---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Opal Design LLC">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection 
      title="Privacy Policy" 
      description="Last updated: June 23, 2025"
    />
    
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose dark:prose-invert prose-headings:font-display prose-headings:font-semibold prose-a:text-primary-600 dark:prose-a:text-primary-400 prose-img:rounded-lg space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
  <p class="lead">
    We value your trust and we treat your information like we’d want ours treated: respectfully, securely, and with no surprises.
  </p>
  <p>This Privacy Policy explains what we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have.</p>

  <h2>1. What We Collect</h2>
  <p>We only collect what we need to do our job well. This may include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your name and email address (when you fill out a form or contact us)</li>
    <li>Details about the service you’re requesting</li>
    <li>Optional info you choose to provide so we can better assist you (like documents or special instructions)</li>
    <li>Basic site usage data (like page views or browser type) to help us understand how our site is being used</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do not collect sensitive data like your location, payment details (those go through secure third-party processors), or anything you haven’t willingly shared.</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use your information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Respond to service requests</li>
    <li>Deliver the services you booked</li>
    <li>Improve our website and offerings</li>
    <li>Occasionally follow up with helpful resources or check-ins but only if it’s relevant</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We never spam, and we don’t sell your data. Ever.</p>

  <h2>3. Cookies &amp; Site Tracking</h2>
  <p>We use basic cookies and analytics (like Google Analytics or privacy-friendly alternatives) to see what’s working and what needs improvement. You can disable cookies in your browser at any time.</p>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We use trusted third-party tools to help run Opal Design LLC. These may include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Form processors (e.g., Formspree or Tally)</li>
    <li>Payment processors (e.g., Stripe or PayPal)</li>
    <li>Email services (e.g., Fastmail or Constant Contact)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>These services only access the data necessary to perform their function, and they’re expected to protect it.</p>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You have full control over your data.</p>
  <p>You can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Ask us what data we’ve collected</li>
    <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
    <li>Ask us to update or delete your information</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To do so, just email us at <a href="mailto:hello.mail@opaldesignllc.com">hello.mail@opaldesignllc.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>6. Data Storage &amp; Security</h2>
  <p>We take data security seriously. We use secure servers and reputable platforms, and we keep things tidy. No unnecessary storage or risky backups.</p>
  <p>If we ever suspect a breach, we’ll notify you promptly and transparently.</p>

  <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>Opal Design LLC is not intended for children under 13. We don’t knowingly collect data from anyone under that age.</p>

  <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>If we ever make big changes, we’ll update this page and clearly note the new date at the top. Minor updates may be made to keep things clear and current.</p>

  <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    Still have questions? Want your data removed? Just want to say hi?<br />
    You can reach us at: <a href="mailto:hello.mail@opaldesignllc.com">hello.mail@opaldesignllc.com</a>
  </p>
</div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout> 
